A suspected chicken thief was stoned to death in Majengo village in Lumakanda sub-county.Witnesses said the suspect was cornered in Majengo market early in the morning carrying the chickens, which were identified by the owner.&nbsp;After raising the alarm, a mob gave chase, cornered the man and stoned him to death. They later dumped his body on the main road before police arrived. &nbsp;Lumakanda OCS William Oyugi warned the residents against mob justice.